{"tid":2514914,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《單人BNO走難篇》申請已批你問我答","createTime":"2021-05-03T14:22:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T16:30:29.000Z","uid":242262,"like":17,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"b5560763fa443dd3cef2b911d8bc43de0bb0348b","tid":2514914,"uid":242262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T14:22:53.000Z","msg":"香港單人獨立申請<br />\n等左2個月先批，等到灰左<br />\n離當初填既出發日期前3日終於等到<br />\n<br />\n有咩想知除左會自爆既野，只要你問我都盡答<br />\n<br />\n順便宣傳下TG<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBHK Channel <br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/britonshk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fbritonshk&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOGHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=ffa5c3c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/britonshk</a><br />\n <br />\nBHK 英戰線 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/joinchat/WMwoCuzwFJyG_TxC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FWMwoCuzwFJyG_TxC&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOGHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=ad7c4ffb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/joinchat/WMwoCuzwFJyG_TxC</a><br />\n<br />\nBHK 英戰線 HK/UK 公海<br />\n用途：自由的討論區。"},{"pid":"85ba89b172b43a5e22d0e9a0c36070f8833a3712","tid":2514914,"uid":299514,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T14:37:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a40192236302f7adb3c7b5006d851b751259c07","tid":2514914,"uid":375068,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T14:39:32.000Z","msg":"唔批都唔買得機票住<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bec5bce5fc1b3159b379853d011203b82afcb8c2","tid":2514914,"uid":242262,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"85ba89b172b43a5e22d0e9a0c36070f8833a3712","tid":2514914,"uid":299514,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T14:37:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T14:50:55.000Z","msg":"去北角申請果d要限批出後90日內去<br />\n<br />\n用App申請雖沒抵埗限期，但要注意簽證有效日期<br />\n<br />\n但這不代表申請人可以將簽證無限期放床下底、慢慢先去。因為簽證仍是有30個月或5年的有效期。如果你用App成功申請簽證，但未能在180日之內出發的話，這樣你就不能滿足5年內、每12月不可離開英國超過180天之申請永居（indefinite leave to remain／settlement）要求，你的簽證到期後就要再續簽（extend）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20210202/UVDNQ4JCHBHWBANTKIJMYXIVPQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20210202%2FUVDNQ4JCHBHWBANTKIJMYXIVPQ%2F&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOGHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=6c787227\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20210202%2FUVDNQ4JCHBHWBANTKIJMYXIVPQ%2F&h=b0524ae3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20210202/UVDNQ4JCHBHWBANTKIJMYXIVPQ/</a>"},{"pid":"53fd137966d76ccb5da723fc0a58cebd3373a3bb","tid":2514914,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T14:52:14.000Z","msg":"身家 ?"},{"pid":"b594883bbae36ad4d87cc5d72d3e3b00e83c4ce6","tid":2514914,"uid":52619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T14:57:33.000Z","msg":"身家 年齡 學歷 英語程度 到步之後點生活   大約就得,唔洗自爆<br />\n純參考下,今年內應該到我搞"},{"pid":"a08b40cac45e3edc3c23e4b44597934a6653fd37","tid":2514914,"uid":242262,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"53fd137966d76ccb5da723fc0a58cebd3373a3bb","tid":2514914,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T14:52:14.000Z","msg":"身家 ?"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T15:01:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a68f5be18d1b157a184a7a48bd306bdb281a01e","tid":2514914,"uid":228955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T15:01:57.000Z","msg":"Goodluck"},{"pid":"972bd29f4fa283723f8102cbd19dda54a7045494","tid":2514914,"uid":242262,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b594883bbae36ad4d87cc5d72d3e3b00e83c4ce6","tid":2514914,"uid":52619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-0